name: Canyon Road Turquoise Charms Necklace
description:
Canyon roads and bright western sunlight inspired this necklace made of Turquoise adorned with charms handcrafted from Fine (.999 pure) Silver. The beads are knotted in cord and suspended from Sterling Silver chain. Undoubtedly a piece to invoke inspired exploration.

A sultry layering piece or striking on its own.

* crafted of High Quality Sterling & Fine silver
* 17.75 inches | Long charm is roughly 1" long
* comes elegantly packaged & ready to gift
* handcrafted in my oregon stringofblue studio

An extender can be purchased at an additional cost.
